Label: CCAN:DNA:CASC5
Comment: The mechanism of interaction between the CENPH-I Complex and the centromeric nucleosome (containing CENPA) is unknown. The CENH-I complex is observed to interact with the centromeric core throughout the cell cycle.

Label: complex
Comment: The Mis18 complex binds the centromere in late telophase/early G1 phase. The mechanism of interaction between the Mis18 complex and the centromeric core is unknown.
